Louie Mynx, a cat,
Chillin' in a cozy hoodie,
Purrs with carefree glee.

Hoodie's snug embrace,
Louie lounges with such grace,
Whiskers twitch in spree.

Feline fashionista,

Whimsy on display.

In the moonlit night,
Louie's hoodie shines so bright,
Feline fun takes flight.
